{
  "stem": "894.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father had a sister who lived in the city, with her husband and her grown daughter in a very lovely little house that was always, I remember, so spotless.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we heard that they were going to take them away the next day because the husband was Polish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, at that point, we were not told yet anything about being taken away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was told in the evening that they're going to take them away tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I remember getting up very, very early in the morning and running to their house, just to see them before they leave.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember looking in the door and seeing a spotless kitchen-- everything just perfectly left.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were gone because he was Polish?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't do the shopping.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know how it got to the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would imagine that they allowed you certain hours to go out and shop.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the currency was the Hungarian currency.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, that didn't change.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm not aware of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was in her own city, which was quite a distance from us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they just started rounding up the Jews to take them away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [CRYING]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I need a minute.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, so they-- they took some-- they took groups.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These streets, they'll take today, and then-- I remember they took away, maybe for two days, some Jews, and then it was our turn.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] they lined us up in the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was an elderly man who was, like, a very important man in town-- very aristocratic family.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
